      Model Name
      Breeze 5
      • 25W HD stereo sound: With Portronics Breeze 5, a 25W speaker, enjoy a delightful sound experience and feel richness and clarity in every beat. The compact size of this mini speaker makes it portable and travel-friendly so you can take it with you, wherever you go.
      • RGB LED Lights: These 25-watt party speakers transform any space into a colorful haven with RGB lights. These dynamic lights come in 3 modes that follow your music's beats, adding a sparkling touch to any occasion, be it a chill session or a hangout with friends.
      • Hands-Free Calling On-the-Go: Stay connected effortlessly with hands-free calling using the built-in wireless microphone. Answer calls with a simple button press, making this speakers for home convenient for multitasking while enjoying your music.
      • Flexible Connections for Versatile Enjoyment: Connect your device to the speaker seamlessly with Bluetooth 5.3v, Micro SD Card, AUX, and USB options for uninterrupted, HQ sound. The bluetooth speaker also has built-in FM providing a versatile listening experience.
      • TWS Pairing for Dual Sound Output: Take your audio experience to the next level by pairing two Breeze 5 speakers wirelessly. Enjoy double sound output at 50 watts, creating a powerful and immersive audio environment for both indoor and outdoor settings.
      • 6-Hour Playback: Keep the music playing with this bluetooth speakers impressive 6-hour playtime. Charge effortlessly using the included Type-C cable for extended use. The Lithium battery ensures your speaker is ready for long trips, hikes, and parties.
      • IPX5 Water Resistant: The speaker has IPX5 water resistance, ensuring exceptional durability. Its splash-resistant feature allows you to enjoy music in light rain or poolside. Ideal for outdoor activities like the beach or camping, enjoy worry-free music anytime.

          Additional details

          Get ready for a sound party with Portronics Breeze 5! This 25W mini speaker delivers rich and clear beats, making your music experience delightful. Plus, it's small and easy to carry, so take it with you wherever you go. The fun doesn't stop there the built-in RGB lights turn any place into a colorful party zone with three cool modes. Need to take a call? No worries! The wireless microphone makes it a breeze. Connect your device easily with Bluetooth, Micro SD Card, AUX, or USB for top-notch sound. Pair two speakers for double the fun, enjoy 6 hours of playback, and charge effortlessly using the included Type-C cable. It's IPX5 water-resistant for worry-free outdoor jamming!
